<lb n="0283c03" ed="T"/>日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>摩努多覽嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>達
<lb n="0283c04" ed="T"/>里摩<note place="inline">二合</note>誐野乃嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>羯里摩<note place="inline">二合</note>迦魯
<lb n="0283c05" ed="T"/>婆嚩</p>
<lb n="0283c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0283c0601">以二手作金剛拳。誦金剛嬉戲真言。</p>
