<lb n="0283c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0283c1501">復誦內外供養真言。</p>
<lb n="0283c16" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0283c1601">唵<note place="inline">引</note>阿迦<note place="inline">引</note>魯<note place="inline">引</note>目欠薩里嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>達里摩<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0283c17" ed="T"/>拏<note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note>儞也<note place="inline">二合引</note>努怛半<note place="inline">二合</note>曩怛嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note></p>
<lb n="0283c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0283c1801">復作觀想。想自心上出一月輪。輪上有<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0283007" n="0283007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0283007" n="0283007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0283007" n="0283007"/>真<anchor xml:id="end0283007"/>言
<lb n="0283c19" ed="T"/>如華鬘相。各有光明如輪內然燈。及曼拏羅
<lb n="0283c20" ed="T"/>一切賢聖皆有光明如是想已即作持誦。獻
<lb n="0283c21" ed="T"/>閼伽水誦閼伽真言。獻飲食等五種供養誦
<lb n="0283c22" ed="T"/>本真言。如是<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0283008" n="0283008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0283008" n="0283008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0283008" n="0283008"/>訖<anchor xml:id="end0283008"/>已左手<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0283009" n="0283009"/><anchor xml:id="beg0283009" n="0283009"/>執<anchor xml:id="end0283009"/>鈴。誦鈴真言。</p>
