<lb n="0283c27" ed="T"/>野<note place="inline">引</note>嚩覩<note place="inline">引</note>灑尼吽吽吽</p>
<lb n="0283c28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0283c2801">誦此真言已。復用右手<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0283010" n="0283010"/><anchor xml:id="beg0283010" n="0283010"/>擲<anchor xml:id="end0283010"/>金剛杵。誦此真
<lb n="0283c29" ed="T"/>言。</p>
